lead_paragraph: Former U.S. secretary of state Hillary Clinton called Chancellor Angela Merkel "the greatest leader in Europe" during a visit to Berlin on Sunday and said it was high time America had a woman leader too, though without confirming she would seek the job.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton Says Merkel Is Europe's 'Greatest Leader'
headline.print_headline: Hillary Clinton Says Merkel Is Europe's 'Greatest Leader'
